[{"client_msg_id":"d167c000-e6da-46de-bfde-e3534e3615ad","type":"message","user":"U7TMPGWJ0","text":"もしかしたら vim-lsp-settings (vim-lsp自体) で refresh_pattern ってうまく効いてないとかそんな感じあったりしないですかね。 heavenshell さんがハマってる感じっぽいので気になったのですが。僕は vim-lsp な環境だと asyncomplete 使って。あとは元々 iskeyword を設定する流儀ではあるので `$` や `-` や `:` や `@` を言語によって追加してるので問題なさそうではあるのですが。vim-lsp単体でオムニ補完だと入力時や補完開始位置によって補完途切れたりとか発生してそうな雰囲気(ちゃんと試してはいない\n```  autocmd Filetype php setlocal iskeyword+=$\n  autocmd Filetype html,css setlocal iskeyword+=@-@\n  autocmd Filetype html,css setlocal iskeyword+=:\n  autocmd Filetype html,htmldjango,blade,vue,gitcommit setlocal iskeyword+=-```","ts":"1596351871.006200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"xLyA9"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"8435894a-f459-4ad1-a73a-a9cdd1e8264d","type":"message","user":"U7TMPGWJ0","text":"refresh_pattern で設定すれば iskeyword の設定関係なく、よしなにやれるって感じだったとは思うのですが。","ts":"1596351921.006700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"lnB4g"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U018H9XB049","text":"<@U018H9XB049> has joined the channel","ts":"1596355611.007000","subtype":"channel_join","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null},{"type":"message","user":"URP42MS1J","text":"<@URP42MS1J> has joined the channel","ts":"1596355737.007300","subtype":"channel_join","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null},{"client_msg_id":"41842413-9177-4089-B982-3B9F0B2E66CD","type":"message","user":"U78A6ESHM","text":"<https://vim-jp.slack.com/archives/CJMV3MSLR/p1596260764097200|https://vim-jp.slack.com/archives/CJMV3MSLR/p1596260764097200>","ts":"1596357590.007500","attachments":[{"fallback":"[July 31st, 2020 10:46 PM] mattn: refresh-pattern には isk を含めないのがコツです。","id":1,"author_id":"U03C6TEAZ","author_name":"mattn","author_s